snippet.title: [TRAILER] Growth Spurt: A Meandering Intermission into the Afterhours of a Miscalculation
snippet.description:
https://gamesformycomputer.itch.io/growth-spurt
https://gamesformycomputer.itch.io/growth-spurt
https://gamesformycomputer.itch.io/growth-spurt

A faux pas at the Middle School dance reverts Nour back to their primordial state and sends them on a one-night maximalist transformative journey. Flop, slide, leap, and rocket around the city filled with zany future friends and mysterious architectures. Play eclectic mini-games where you will discover whether surgery can be joyful, if aliens have feelings, and how to deal with a bad boss!
